---
// Silica Governance Page - Professional design
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Governance - Silica Protocol" description="Comprehensive governance mechanisms for Silica Protocol - proposals, voting, treasury management, and validator elections">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950 text-white py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Animated Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(14,165,233,0.3) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(14,165,233,0.3) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 blur-[120px] animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 5s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-1/3 left-1/4 w-[350px] h-[350px] rounded-full bg-teal-500/15 blur-[100px] animate-pulse" style="animation-duration: 7s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
          Protocol <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-teal-400 to-green-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Governance</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-cyan-100/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Decentralized decision-making mechanisms that ensure Silica Protocol evolves with community consensus and technical excellence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Governance Overview Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Governance Overview
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Silica Protocol implements a sophisticated governance system that balances technical expertise with community participation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- On-Chain Governance -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-500/40 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/50">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 text-center">On-Chain Governance</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
            All protocol changes are executed through on-chain voting mechanisms, ensuring transparency and immutability.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-2">
            <li>• Proposal submission and voting</li>
            <li>• Automated execution of approved changes</li>
            <li>• Immutable governance history</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Validator Elections -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-teal-500/20 hover:border-teal-500/40 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-teal-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-teal-500/50">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M5 3v4a1 1 0 001 1h4m-4-4l6.414-2.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L19 8m-4-4v4a1 1 0 001 1h4M5 3l6.414 2.586a2 2 0 002.828 0L19 3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 text-center">Validator Elections</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
            Democratic validator selection process that ensures network security and decentralization.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-2">
            <li>• Stake-weighted voting</li>
            <li>• Performance-based selection</li>
            <li>• Regular rotation cycles</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Treasury Management -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-green-500/20 hover:border-green-500/40 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-green-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-green-500/50">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 text-center">Treasury Management</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
            Transparent treasury operations funded by protocol fees and managed through community governance.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-2">
            <li>• Community fund allocation</li>
            <li>• Grant program management</li>
            <li>• Budget approval processes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proposal Process Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Proposal Process
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          How to submit, discuss, and vote on protocol improvements
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Process Steps -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-12">
        <!-- Step 1: Draft -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-cyan-500/20 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-cyan-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/50">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">Draft Proposal</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Create a detailed proposal with technical specifications and rationale</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Discussion -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-teal-500/20 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shadow-lg shadow-teal-500/50">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">Community Discussion</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Engage with the community for feedback and refinement</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Submit -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shadow-lg shadow-green-500/50">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">Submit On-Chain</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Submit the proposal to the governance contract</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Vote -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-emerald-500/20 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/50">4</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3">Community Vote</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Stakeholders vote on the proposal over a voting period</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Voting Requirements -->
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Voting Requirements</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-cyan-400 mb-3">Proposal Threshold</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-300 space-y-2">
              <li>• Minimum 10,000 SILICA deposit</li>
              <li>• Technical review by validators</li>
              <li>• Community discussion period (7 days)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-teal-400 mb-3">Voting Period</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-300 space-y-2">
              <li>• 14-day voting window</li>
              <li>• Quorum requirement: 25% of total stake</li>
              <li>• Approval threshold: 66% majority</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Active Proposals Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Active Proposals
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Current governance proposals open for voting
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Proposal Cards -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Proposal 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">SIP-001: Increase Validator Set Size</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Proposal to expand the active validator set from 100 to 150 nodes</p>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-green-500/30">Active</span>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400">7</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Days Left</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">68%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Yes Votes</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-400">1.2M</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Total Stake</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="#" class="text-cyan-400 font-medium hover:text-cyan-300">View Details →</a>
            <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:from-cyan-600 hover:to-cyan-700 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/30">Vote Now</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Proposal 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-500/20">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">SIP-002: Treasury Allocation for Research</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Allocate 500,000 SILICA for quantum-resistant cryptography research</p>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-green-500/30">Active</span>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="text-center bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400">12</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Days Left</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">54%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Yes Votes</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-400">890K</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Total Stake</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="#" class="text-cyan-400 font-medium hover:text-cyan-300">View Details →</a>
            <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-teal-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:from-teal-600 hover:to-teal-700 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-teal-500/30">Vote Now</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Treasury Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Treasury Overview
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Transparent management of protocol funds for ecosystem development
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Treasury Balance -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Treasury Balance</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-400 mb-4">2,847,392 SILICA</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-6">≈ $1,247,000 USD</div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">Protocol Fees</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-cyan-400">1,234,567 SILICA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">Validator Rewards</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-teal-400">892,345 SILICA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">Community Grants</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-green-400">720,480 SILICA</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Recent Expenditures -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-teal-500/20">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Recent Expenditures</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-white">Security Audit</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Trail of Bits engagement</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="font-medium text-cyan-400">50,000 SILICA</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">2 days ago</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-white">Developer Grants</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Q4 ecosystem funding</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="font-medium text-teal-400">25,000 SILICA</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">1 week ago</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg border border-slate-700">
              <div>
                <div class="font-medium text-white">Marketing Campaign</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Global awareness initiative</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <div class="font-medium text-green-400">15,000 SILICA</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">2 weeks ago</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 via-teal-600 to-green-600 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Animated Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 50px 50px;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Participate in Governance
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8">
        Shape the future of Silica Protocol by participating in governance decisions.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/proposals" class="bg-white text-teal-700 font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
          View All Proposals
        </a>
        <a href="/validators" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white border-2 border-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-teal-700 transition-all duration-300">
          Become a Validator
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>